</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>By overriding these methods in a custom client class and implementing them to return an instance of Lettuce with your own settings, you can make any settings you want.</p>
<p>Can then replace components of the client class by defining components of the custom client class with the same names as the original components.</p>
